text:
Tu to hero banta hai na be
Bhai, next level aadmi hai yaar tu
Tujhse life mein kaafi motivation liya hu
Aakhri ke mahine mein gussa dila hi diya tha tujheðŸ˜‚
Yaar mai tjhe bahut irritate karta hu na
Sorry uske liye, pr tere reaction kaafi mast hote hai, unke liye tera gussa bhi jayas hau
Yaar tere saath volley aur badi bahut yaad aata hai
Har jagah apna full deta hai tu, aur wo bahut mast lagta hai mjhe
Tere saath gym jaana(patches meinðŸ˜…) mein bahut maza aata tha, last mein uske liye nhi jaa paye
Yaar mjhe kisi ke bolne ka itna farak nhi padha, par jab tune dual karaya tab mai second karne laga apni choices ko(that is the amount of influence your choices make on me) 
But overall maza aaya 
Chal ab mai thak gya 
Bye
author: Tushar  Singhal

text:
Ankit bhai kya haal chaal
Yaar teri shaayriyon ka to mai deewana hu
Mast likhta hai bhai, aur thodi vulgar ho to dm karte rehna
Yaar hum har jagah saath the wing mein, Aero mein aur saari bakchodiyan ki hai
Yaar maine aise bahut baar logo se baat ki hai, aur sab yahi kehte the aur hai
Ki tere ko wing se nhi nikalna chaiye tha, hamari alag hi level ki bonding hoti nhi to
Par fir bhi wo assignment waale din, exam nights, wing treats, gpl kya nhi kiya saath mein
Yaar tu bahut innocent aur helpful hai, tera jaisa yaar sabko mile, bahut madad ki hai tune meri
Baaki aap to ab bade aadmi ban jaoge
Abhi se registry kar rha hu, saare kaamo ke liye
Baad mein kabhi koi appointment lene ke liye bola to yahi dikha dunga
#IAS
Chal ab mai tera saara pyaar thukrata hu
Ab apna inteqaam dikhaðŸ˜‚
author: Tushar  Singhal

text:
Are I P bhaiya kya haal chal
Yaar Civil chodne ka bas ek hi gam tha
Mera saanp wahi chhut gya
Yaar tere saath alag hi masti mein rehta tha mai, kabhi koi chinta hi nhi hoti thi, assig ho ya kuch bhi, Tu sab sambhal leta tha
Aur teri didi ki shaadi, wo hamari wing ki eklauti outing thi saath mein, all because of you
Yaar last ke mahine mein aana chaiye the, bahut yaad kiya tjhe
Yaar wo TA202 ki yaadein, ohooo
Beta karna to aapko hi hai
Aur bsdk ne sahi mein hum par hi chodd diya
Wo raat bhar cad banana
Wo Gupta ki saath mein bitching karna
Tu hamesha kam neend mein rehta tha, busy aadmi tha na, par kam neend waala ip mjhe bahut pasand tha
Yaar mjhe yaad hai, tune mjhe saanp bolna start kiya tha, kyuki mai ne tujhe ditch kiya tha kahi to, par bc fir tu hi saanp ho gya sabke liye
Wo bahut mast tha
Par bahut maza aayega
Mai kanpur aaunga, to mehman nawazi ke liye taiyaar rehna, aur haan dusri didi ki bhi to shaadi hai, usme bhi bulana 
Chal byeðŸ˜˜
author: Tushar  Singhal

text:
Hello Sir, 
Kaise hai aap
Yaar aap to mere liye bhagwaan ke saman ho
Aap kuch bhi karna, bas mera saath mat chodna
Sabki life ek source of constant motivation hota hai, like a pillar, you are that for me
Whenever I was in dilemma Or self doubt you have been always there for me
Aap kabhi doubtful hote the to mai college fuse ho jaata tha, ki ab mera kya hoga
One of the best thing that happened with me is ki aap meri life mein abhi present rahoge, usse alag hi level ka satisfaction rehta hai mjheðŸ˜…
Yaad hai hamari pehli baar 3 top ke grp par ladai hui thi, jab aapne mjhe pig bola tha
Tab hai aur aaj, mai aapko chah kar bhi amr sant nhi bol pata aur na kisi ko bolte dekh sakta
Kabhi aapke saath course nhi hua, iska kaafi bura lagta hai mjhe, par har course mein aap mere saath the
Okay so hamne kya kya saath kiya hau
Trip par gye the, intern prep, placement prep, badi, volley
Bas ek baat ka regret hai, ki aapke saath aakhri time nhi bita paaya itna, par hum to janamo ke liye saath hau, 1 mahina kya cheez hai
Chalo dhyaan rakhna apna, aur hamara
Byeeee
author: Tushar  Singhal
